BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:dcef-churchtomorrow-2026@dcepiscopalfellowship.org
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260420T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260420T210000
SUMMARY:Becoming the Church of Tomorrow
DESCRIPTION:Join Bishop Mariann Budde and Canon Stephanie Spellers for an
  evening of worship\, food\, and great conversation! Spellers' latest book\,
  Church Tomorrow?\, wrestles with the decline of traditional religion\, the
  wisdom of nonreligious Millennials and Gen Zs\, and our call to be
  courageous witnesses for the God of love.
URL:https://stephaniespellers.com/church-tomorrow
CATEGORIES:UPCOMING
X-IMAGE:images/7279785fdcf6480d426751609e40a6fb.jpg
END:VEVENT

